name: Clouds And Me
body:
At Clouds And Me, we focus on creating value by discovering the intersection of your interests and the real world around you, through which the Clouds And Me Engine can make personalized recommendations across any number of fields.  We are building an evolutionary harmonization engine for this purpose. We can be engaged for projects and to design solutions for problems in the world. We can also be contacted for web application consulting on the front or back end.


### Support or Contact
